'''{{ill|Hyūga no Shikinai-sha Ichiran|de|Hyūga no Shikinai-sha Ichiran|ja|日向国の式内社一覧|zh|Hyūga no Shikinai-sha Ichiran|lt=Hyūga no Shikinai-sha Ichiran|lt_ja=日向国の式内社一覧|lt_de=Hyūga no Shikinai-sha Ichiran|lt_zh=Hyūga no Shikinai-sha Ichiran}}''' (日向国の式内社一覧) is a list of {{ill|Shinto Shrines|de|Shinto Shrines|ja|神社|zh|Shinto Shrines}} classified under {{ill|Hyūga Province|de|Hyūga Province|ja|日向国|zh|Hyūga Province}}, drawn from those shrines recorded in volumes 9 and 10 – "Kami Name Register, Upper and Lower" – of the {{ill|Engishiki|de|Engishiki|ja|Engishiki|zh|Engishiki}} ({{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|zh|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|lt=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|lt_ja=延喜式神名帳|lt_de=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|lt_zh=Engishiki Jinmyōchō}}) as well as the so‐called {{ill|Shikinaisha|de|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|zh|Shikinaisha}} and their associated {{ill|Candidate Shrines|de|Candidate Shrines|ja|論社|zh|Candidate Shrines}}.

また『延喜式』神名帳の編纂当時に存在したが、同帳に記載の無い神社、いわゆる {{ill|Shikigaisha|de|Shikigaisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|zh|Shikigaisha}} についても付記する。

